Following code uses regex to find all sub strings that matches pattern. I used `f.find(i)` and set `i` in loop to include overlapped white space after each found sub strings.
 

    List&lt;String&gt; findAll3LetterWords(String sentence){   
        List&lt;String&gt; allMatches = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;();
        Matcher m = Pattern.compile(&quot;\\s[^\\s]{3}\\s&quot;)
                    .matcher(&quot; &quot;+sentence+&quot; &quot;);
        int i = 0;
        while(m.find(i)) {
            allMatches.add(m.group().trim());
            i = m.start() + 1;
        }
        return allMatches;
    }

